---
import Card from "../Card/index.astro";
---

<Card colSpan="sm:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1" rowSpan="md:row-span-2 lg:row-span-6 " title="hello! 👋🏻">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 text-2xl">
    <div class="text-base font-light">
      <p>
        I am Enoch, a data enthusiast from the <a class="text-red-400 capitalize italic font-semibold" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Little_red_dot">little red dot 🔴</a>.
        <br />
        Finding trends, and making predictions using machine learning models are kinda my thing!
        <br />
    </div>
    <p class="text-base ">
      I love meddling with technologies to automate and upgrade my life. I have built Telegram bots, upgraded PCs and laptops, and set up a home lab with ad-blocking!
      <br />
      <br />
      I plan to set up a NAS for backing up my photos and also to host my own website in the future! 
    </p>
    <p class="text-base font-light">
      When I am not coding, I am either playing with my cat 🐱, training/coaching ultimate frisbee 🥏 or just enjoying a cup of coffee ☕️. 
    </p>
  </div>
</Card>
